# Plugin Sync After Edit

**When you edit any file in `/Users/ranmor/Documents/FigDex Codex/plugin/`**, after saving the changes run:

```bash
rsync -av --exclude='.DS_Store' --exclude='*.backup' --exclude='_archive' "/Users/ranmor/Documents/FigDex Codex/plugin/" "/Users/ranmor/My Drive (ran.3dcube@gmail.com) (1)/FigDex Plugin - latest version/"
```

This keeps a synced copy at `My Drive/FigDex Plugin - latest version/`.

To change the target path, edit this rule.
